<span id="freeTextContainer15282147070329794273">Rather disappointing. I picked this book up at a book sale for a song, mostly because the cover advertised the book as &quot;Agatha Christie&apos;s Crown Princess&quot; and being a Christie fan I thought I&apos;d try it out. The story was long, boring, and the mystery easy to figure out. Very few of the characters had any appeal to me and quite honestly, I skipped parts just to get through to the end. Sorry to say, I don&apos;t think I&apos;ll try any more of PD James&apos;s books.</span>
  <span id="freeText15282147070329794273" style="display:none">Rather disappointing. I picked this book up at a book sale for a song, mostly because the cover advertised the book as "Agatha Christie's Crown Princess" and being a Christie fan I thought I'd try it out. The story was long, boring, and the mystery easy to figure out. Very few of the characters had any appeal to me and quite honestly, I skipped parts just to get through to the end. Sorry to say, I don't think I'll try any more of PD James's books.</span>
